snippet.title: 3D Maze Man: Adventures in Winter Wonderland
snippet.description:
A christmas release of '3d Maze Man' (a pac-man clone) that came out in 1998.

If anyone has any info on '3D Ms. Maze: Tropical Adventures'; screenshots, videos or even the game I would really appreciate it if you could link it to me.
